name: kaiser-grafix
overview:
kaiser-grafix consists of a team of ten selected specialists, including graphic artists and illustrators, sound engineers and programmers. We specialize in animated cartoons, web development, print design, corporate identity, newsletter marketing and search engine optimization.

The headquarters of kaiser-grafix is located in the center of Freiburg. We develop and create ideas in close cooperation with our clients to find the perfect solution – modern, current and professional.
